steps.name: Given  Launch Fieldnet Dev application to Enter UserID and Password click Next 0
$("By.xpath: //h2[text()='Verify with your password']//following::input[1]") should be([exist, 10 s.])
And  click SubmitNewBusiness Menu and Enter ProducerID and click search
And  click on Plus icon to select Environment and click continue
When  EzApp is launched and user enters VUL Insured details state and UL product
And  User Fills VUL LifeCase setup screen and NewYorkRegsixty when state is NY and click on Next
$("By.xpath: //select[@id='lb_322' or @name='lb_322']") select option containing text(Resident U.S. citizen)
And  User Fills VUL Primary Insured and Primary Insured Cont screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills All VUL Personal History Information screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Product Screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Purpose of Insurance Screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Owner and Life Owner cont screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills EntityOwner and Trust Certification details Screen and click Next
$("By.xpath: //h1[contains(text(),'Certification of Trust Agreement - Owner')]") is displayed()
$("By.xpath: //select[@alt_id='Type']") select option containing text(Individual other than Insured)
$("By.xpath: //select[@alt_id='CitizenshipCountry']") select option containing text(United States of America)
$("By.xpath: //h1[contains(text(),'Certification of Trust Agreement - Owner')]") is displayed()
$("By.xpath: //select[@alt_id='SigningTrustees']") select option containing text(a Majority of authorized Trustees)
And  User Fills VUL Life Beneficiaries and Other Coverage screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Payment Information and Certification screen details and click on Next
$("By.xpath: //label[text()='Is initial premium being submitted with this Application?']//following::div[1]") is displayed()
$("By.xpath: //label[text()='Premium Payor']//following::select[1]") select option containing text(Proposed Insured(s))
$("By.xpath: //label[text()='Does the Premium Payor’s source of premium include a loan or premium financing?']//following::div[1]") is displayed()
And  User Fills VUL HIV consent screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills VUL Life Producer Statement screen details and click on Next
$("By.xpath: //label[text()='Risk classification presented to client:']//following::select[1]") should be([exist, 30 s.])
$("By.xpath: //label[text()='Risk classification presented to client:']//following::select[1]") select option containing text(Non-Tobacco)
And  User Fills VUL Life Producer Compensation screen details and click on Next
$("By.xpath: //select[@id='lb_4']") select option containing text(Dollar Cost Averaging)
$("By.xpath: //select[@id='lb_327']") select option containing text(Specialty - MML Equity Rotation)
$("By.xpath: //select[@id='lb_155' or @name='lb_155']") select option containing text(Specialty - Fidelity® VIP Health Care)
$("By.xpath: //select[@id='lb_66']") select option containing text(Income with Limited Growth)
$("By.xpath: //select[@id='lb_67']") select option containing text(Near Term (less than 1 year))
$("By.xpath: //select[@alt_id='APerson_Country']") select option containing text(United States of America)
